Requirements for Basketball England Registrationpage

Write and execute testcases using Cucumber and Selenium on the Basketball England page.
Every testcase shall have atleast one Junit-assert
The feature-file should be created using BDD* and be explained.
The feature-file should be connected to Selenium Webdriver-code

The testcases must contain atleast one Scenario Outline.
The testcases should be run on atleast two different browsers.
Create atleast one private method that is using explicit wait.

The testcase shall cover:
 * Creating an account successfully
 * Create an account - missing lastname
 * Create an account - Not matching password
 * Create an account - Terms and conditions not accepted


 * Behavioral Driven Deployment


